{"title":"听红线女演唱会","authors":["许士杰"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"听红线女演唱会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许士杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八八年九月二十八日晚，红线女在北京人民剧场作演唱会首场演出。“红腔”飘逸隽永，给首都观众以美的享受。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红腔润脆动京华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三日绕梁入万家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂得荔枝莹似玉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岭南塞北竞繁花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疑是丝丝荡笛萧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空秋雁撩心潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幽香缕缕人如醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫声情上碧霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三飞流直泻溅珍珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔放回旋音韵殊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激越戛然情未尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华灯明月照清渠。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}